[R18] {'review_id': 'jiS7qyI3YxVAIv8scJSMMw', 'user_id': '_bhygbIGZz51CPzUzKT2bA', 'business_id': 'JtDZvV3HddxFnNdrwrWh7g', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Absolutely delicious! The food was so good I forgot to take pictures! Their red sauce is to die for, we also got a seafood pasta with squid ink lingo I with crab and shrimp that was incredible. I had a craving for veal parm and even though it wasn't on the menu they made one for me and it did not disappoint! So tender it literally fell off the bone, it cut with a butter knife. The outdoor set up was so sweet and the service was top notch! The staff made us (and my dog) feel so welcome. Amazing experience all around, will absolutely be coming back and you should 100% eat dinner here", 'date': '2020-11-07 01:12:46', 'user': {'name': 'Mara', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2016-09-21 16:21:04', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.2, 'fans': 0}}
[R19] {'review_id': 'rnFLaF-Zqa3t9xPVWfB5lQ', 'user_id': 'yS0qfZmG3VXzOgdj-Kh6iA', 'business_id': 'JtDZvV3HddxFnNdrwrWh7g', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Beautiful place. We were late at night almost at the closing hour but nonetheless, they invited us in. The Calamari Fritti was really good. The Tortelloni al Tartufo was delicious and although I would have liked a little bit more of a punch of flavor they were really good. The service was professional, friendly, and prompt. July 2019.', 'date': '2020-10-27 03:26:16', 'user': {'name': 'Sandra', 'review_count': 5, 'yelping_since': '2018-09-17 16:53:32', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.2, 'fans': 0}}
[R20] {'review_id': 'tuIksX3lM2rvIB05JnqGuw', 'user_id': 'a_bI4YSG4i-XlcVT1yhvdw', 'business_id': 'JtDZvV3HddxFnNdrwrWh7g', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "We are very hesitant about outdoor dining these days but decided to try Aroma because the tables looked safe and pleasant. We were very comfortable, the food was delicious, and the service was pleasant. The waiters didn't hover which is better in this environment, we felt safe and really enjoyed our night out. It is bring your own which we prefer. I highly recommend and we will go back if there is another warm enough evening.", 'date': '2020-10-08 12:39:58', 'user': {'name': 'Louise', 'review_count': 14, 'yelping_since': '2015-01-11 20:01:40', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.57, 'fans': 0}}
[R21] {'review_id': 'Wa8oqAy9gVoVdnKFYFsgsg', 'user_id': '4nQBFlejXxqod7_VRGaXjw', 'business_id': 'JtDZvV3HddxFnNdrwrWh7g', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Took our family to Aroma to celebrate our daughter's birthday and what a good choice we made!  Everything was wonderful from start to finish. We started with some appetizers, myself getting the special Calabrese. It was perfect.  I can not go there without getting the Cioppino, so delicious every single time. Never disappoints. Service was outstanding, especially under the current conditions. Thank you Aroma for a wonderful night!", 'date': '2020-10-08 12:06:39', 'user': {'name': 'Donna', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2019-12-15 23:57:12', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
