[R47] {'review_id': 'g6bob_AEvDtWviT0pLWfuA', 'user_id': 'VW3qosqXeFq6QJ4foHkcpw', 'business_id': 'BIxkykL8meGkcNszRNWSyA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 2, 'text': "I almost wish I didn't discover this place- because boxed pasta will never be the same. We found out during a walk in Little Italy (aka trying to walk off a Paesano's food coma) and realized we had nothing planned for dinner.

